Type: Package
Package: jjstatsplot
Title: Wrapper for 'ggstatsplot'
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2026-07-13
Authors@R: person(given = "Serdar", family = "Balci", role = c("aut",
        "cre", "cph"), email = "serdarbalci@serdarbalci.com", comment =
        c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7852-3851"))
Maintainer: Serdar Balci <serdarbalci@serdarbalci.com>
Description: Comprehensive statistical visualization package for jamovi
        that wraps ggstatsplot functions and provides 17+ analysis
        types including histograms, scatter plots, correlation
        matrices, between/within-group comparisons, bar charts, pie
        charts, waffle charts, raincloud plots, ridge plots, arc
        diagrams, lollipop charts, line charts, and segmented bar
        charts. Features automatic plot selection, dual-mode operation
        (single/grouped variables), statistical annotations, and
        publication-ready visualizations with point-and-click
        interface. For comments, suggestions, feature requests or reporting bugs,
        please open an issue at <https://github.com/sbalci/ClinicoPathJamoviModule/issues/>.
